\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\mu}\left(P_{1}\tensor*[_{\mathscr{O}}]{+}{}P_{2}\right)\subseteq\bar{\mu}\left(P_{1}\right)\tensor*[_{\mathscr{I}}]{+}{}\bar{\mu}\left(P_{2}\right)$
